data.text:
Award 1 March 2021

Oxford MP (Anneliese Dodds) thanks SYRCOX.

Oxford MP (Anneliese Dodds) thanks all of the Syrian Community volunteers for their hard work and a brilliant job supporting the local community.

Award 2 November 2021

High Sheriff Award

This award was made by The High Sheriff of Oxfordshire to Hadi Nuri (Founder and Director of Syrcox) in recognition of great and valuable service to Oxfordshire’s community during the Covid 19 pandemic.
